---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---
<BaseLayout title="Amplified Event Strategy" bodyClass="home-page">
  <header class="container-fluid header">
    <div class="row">
      <div class="col">
        <div class="extra-lg-text">
          <span>Global Events.</span><br />
          <span>Exceptional</span><br />
          <span>Experiences.</span><br />
          <span>Delivered.</span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="header-stats">
      <div class="header-stat">
        <span class="stat-number">100+</span>
        <span class="stat-label">Events Produced</span>
      </div>
      <div class="header-stat">
        <span class="stat-number">10+</span>
        <span class="stat-label">Years in Crypto</span>
      </div>
      <div class="header-stat">
        <span class="stat-number">Global</span>
        <span class="stat-label">Reach</span>
      </div>
      <div class="header-stat">
        <span class="stat-number">Since 2015</span>
        <span class="stat-label">Industry Leaders</span>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="scroll-indicator">
      <div class="scroll-line"></div>
    </div>
  </header>

  <div class="container-fluid box-content box-content-short">
    <div class="row">
      <div class="col-md-6">
        <div class="boxy c1-color">
          <div class="row">
            <div class="col">
              <h1 class="title">Global Event<br />Experience</h1>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="row">
            <div class="col">
              <div class="text">
                <p>We've produced events across the globe, giving us an extensive network of professional connections. Over our decades of experience both inside and outside of crypto, we've worked in Asia, South and Central America, across Europe and the United States.</p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="col-md-6">
        <div class="boxy img-box">
          <div class="img"><img src="/images/work3.png" alt="" /></div>
          <div class="bottom-text">
            <div class="link">VIEW THIS PROJECT</div>
            <div class="text">BREAK POINT 2022</div>
          </div>
          <a href="/work/Breakpoint2022.astro" class="project-link-full"></a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="container-fluid box-content box-content-short">
    <div class="row">
      <div class="col-md-6">
        <div class="boxy img-box">
          <div class="img"><img src="/images/work2.png" alt="" /></div>
          <div class="bottom-text">
            <div class="link">VIEW THIS PROJECT</div>
            <div class="text">ONDO SUMMIT 2025</div>
          </div>
          <a href="/work/Ondosummit2025.astro" class="project-link-full"></a>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="col-md-6">
        <div class="boxy primary-color">
          <div class="row">
            <div class="col">
              <h1 class="title">Large Scale<br />Events</h1>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="row">
            <div class="col">
              <div class="text">
                <p>We have produced some of the largest events for 11+ years—the longest standing crypto events producers in the business. We've run events as large as 8,000 delegates, with 500+ speakers and 5 venues concurrently.</p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="container-fluid box-content box-content-short">
    <div class="row">
      <div class="col-md-6">
        <div class="boxy default-color">
          <div class="row">
            <div class="col">
              <h1 class="title">High Profile<br />Speakers</h1>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="row">
            <div class="col">
              <div class="text">
                <p>Throughout our careers, we have produced shows with major high profile speakers from Fortune 100 companies as well as Heads of State, members of congress, headlining entertainers, and more.</p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="col-md-6">
        <div class="boxy img-box">
          <div class="img"><img src="/images/work5.png" alt="" /></div>
          <div class="bottom-text">
            <div class="link">VIEW THIS PROJECT</div>
            <div class="text">HEDERACON 2025</div>
          </div>
          <a href="/work/Hederacon2025.astro" class="project-link-full"></a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="container-fluid box-content box-content-short">
    <div class="row">
      <div class="col-md-6">
        <div class="boxy img-box">
          <div class="img"><img src="/images/work6.png" alt="" /></div>
          <div class="bottom-text">
            <div class="link">VIEW THIS PROJECT</div>
            <div class="text">NEARCON 2024</div>
          </div>
          <a href="/work/Nearcon2024.astro" class="project-link-full"></a>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="col-md-6">
        <div class="boxy c2-color">
          <div class="row">
            <div class="col">
              <h1 class="title">Trusted & Reliable Partners</h1>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="row">
            <div class="col">
              <div class="text">
                <p>We have worked directly with the founders from top projects in the space. Their trust in our team to deliver consistent results helps us maintain clients year-over-year.</p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="container-fluid default-content services-content">
    <div class="row">
      <div class="col">
        <div class="lg-text">
          <span>Our Agency Services<br />& Offerings</span>
        </div>
        <div class="normal-text">
          <p>We are a full-service events agency with global event experience.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="services-list">
          <ul class="services-list__col">
            <li>Event Planning, Strategy and Execution</li>
            <li>Venue Research, Negotiation and Contracting</li>
            <li>Vendor Vetting / Sourcing and Due Diligence for All Event Management Needs</li>
            <li>Event Design / Floor Plans / Renderings</li>
            <li>Production / AV / Stage Design</li>
            <li>Event Budgeting / Revenue Model Scenario Planning</li>
            <li>Registration Strategy and Onsite Execution</li>
          </ul>
          <ul class="services-list__col">
            <li>Sponsorship Strategy, Sales and Execution</li>
            <li>Content Development / Agenda Planning</li>
            <li>Speaker Management / Content Production</li>
            <li>Onsite Production / Rehearsals / Execution</li>
            <li>Catering Management</li>
            <li>Swag Design / Production / Distribution</li>
            <li>Closing Party & After Party Planning / Entertainment Booking</li>
            <li>Signage and Design Planning</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
        <div class="btn-holder">
          <a href="/about" class="cr-btn primary">more about us</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="container-fluid clients-section">
    <div class="row">
      <div class="col">
        <div class="lg-text">
          <span>DELIGHTING OUR</span><br />
          <span>CLIENTS IS OUR</span><br />
          <span>MISSION.</span>
        </div>
        <div class="normal-text">
          <p>There’s no other Web3 event agency who
has produced more large-scale
cryptocurrency events than us!
We’ve partnered with some of the top event
organizers and projects in the
cryptocurrency space since 2015.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="clients-logos">
          <div class="logo-holder"><img src="/images/client1.png" alt="" /></div>
          <div class="logo-holder"><img src="/images/client2.png" alt="" /></div>
          <div class="logo-holder"><img src="/images/client3.png" alt="" /></div>
          <div class="logo-holder"><img src="/images/client4.png" alt="" /></div>
          <div class="logo-holder"><img src="/images/client5.png" alt="" /></div>
          <div class="logo-holder"><img src="/images/client6.png" alt="" /></div>
          <div class="logo-holder"><img src="/images/client7.png" alt="" /></div>
          <div class="logo-holder"><img src="/images/client8.png" alt="" /></div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

</BaseLayout>
